cut all communication,

00:04.601 --> 00:05.702
they'll be sitting ducks.

00:05.750 --> 00:07.968
Tons of jewelry, tons of cash.

00:08.031 --> 00:09.328
What about satellite phones?

00:09.384 --> 00:10.672
Craig got a Shoghi jammer.

00:10.720 --> 00:12.587
You just don't like it
because I thought of it.

00:12.635 --> 00:14.913
