when I'm not OD'ing?

05:08.422 --> 05:10.582
You know, I said
I was sorry, all right?

05:10.800 --> 05:11.996
Who's she?

05:12.136 --> 05:16.402
Uh, yeah, this is Nicky.
Nicky... Renn.

05:18.964 --> 05:20.410
Hi.

05:23.465 --> 05:26.324
You know, you should watch your
shit around him, sweetheart.

05:26.690 --> 05:29.077
In the end,
he's not worth the ride.

05:30.604 --> 05:32.072
Believe me.

05:40.164 --> 05:41.565
Old friend.

05:43.558 --> 05:45.503
All right, so you know what
you're doing, right?

05:45.613 --> 05:48.363
3:00, and then you send me
a text message, okay?

05:51.948 --> 05:54.839
Yeah! Jesus.

06:01.069 --> 06:02.537
We alone?

06:02.687 --> 06:04.038
Yeah.

06:04.335 --> 06:06.646
Hey, listen, traffic up
to Newport's gonna be a bitch.

06:06.694 --> 06:08.097
We should probably
leave early.

06:13.786 --> 06:15.295
What?

06:17.028 --> 06:19.007
I didn't sleep.

06:19.758 --> 06:21.208
Okay. You want some coffee?

06:21.256 --> 06:23.710
We shouldn't be bringing
outsiders in on this job.

06:23.804 --> 06:25.293
It's a bad idea.

06:25.421 --> 06:27.129
Pope, it is the day of, man.

06:27.234 --> 06:30.032
We cannot do this shit right now.
Marco? Really?

06:31.599 --> 06:32.905
You been talking to Baz?

06:33.007 --> 06:35.223
- Is he getting in your head?
- I can size up a job on my own.

06:35.270 --> 06:37.327
Okay. Well, then you know that
every job has its own risks.

06:37.374 --> 06:38.570
Nicky?

06:38.686 --> 06:40.929
You can't tell me
you were cool with that.

06:41.763 --> 06:42.867
Pope...

06:45.491 --> 06:48.668
Look, Craig has put his ass
on the line

06:48.866 --> 06:50.552
a thousand times for you
and Baz.

06:50.585 --> 06:52.354
This isn't about that.

06:55.884 --> 06:57.786
What do you want me
to do, Pope?

07:00.265 --> 07:03.131
I mean, this...
This thing's happening,

07:03.421 --> 07:05.033
with or without you.

07:07.235 --> 07:09.749
Craig needs this.

07:10.265 --> 07:11.639
We owe him.

07:32.446 --> 07:34.703
Hey. That a new car?

07:34.969 --> 07:36.803
Yeah.

07:39.890 --> 07:42.137
Hola.
Hi.

07:44.406 --> 07:48.476
Shouldn't you be on your way
to Craig's, big, uh, boat job?

07:51.562 --> 07:53.631
Why didn't you tell me
we were ripping off Smurf?

07:56.734 --> 07:58.386
She was grilling you
about it?

07:58.515 --> 08:00.577
Yeah.
She thinks I'm involved.

08:01.202 --> 08:02.866
You were.

08:03.632 --> 08:05.312
She really pissed?

08:05.577 --> 08:07.562
She was drinking
at 9:00 a.m.

08:10.225 --> 08:12.265
Nothing new about that.

08:13.839 --> 08:16.101
I know that you went back
without me, Baz.

08:18.788 --> 08:20.913
You were following me?

08:21.515 --> 08:22.960
Man.

08:23.143 --> 08:25.078
You're getting better
at this.

08:25.687 --> 08:27.827
How much?

08:28.143 --> 08:30.765
Uh, a lot.

08:31.034 --> 08:32.999
She's been stealing from us
for years.

08:33.155 --> 08:34.898
You gonna tell the others?

08:35.131 --> 08:37.679
Well, that money belongs
to all of us,

08:38.195 --> 08:39.394
even you.

08:41.258 --> 08:42.717
We're a family.

08:46.168 --> 08:48.780
You should've told me what
we were doing, Baz.

08:49.280 --> 08:51.116
Well...

08:51.785 --> 08:53.887
I didn't know if I could
trust you.

08:58.546 --> 09:01.195
I guess we're gonna
find out now.

09:24.739 --> 09:27.107
Who robbed my unit?

09:27.303 --> 09:28.643
Y-you were robbed?

09:32.532 --> 09:34.998
Your boss seems too stupid,

09:35.185 --> 09:38.320
but you look like the type guy
who thinks he's smart.

09:38.521 --> 09:40.700
Lady, I swear, I had nothing
to do with it, okay?

09:42.513 --> 09:45.545
Now I can do this all day.

09:45.593 --> 09:46.709
Sit up.

09:51.607 --> 09:54.736
A guy paid me to tell him
which unit was yours.

09:55.162 --> 09:57.939
See? Now that wasn't so hard,
was it?

10:03.568 --> 10:05.280
Did he look like this?

10:08.745 --> 10:10.146
Yeah, that's him.

10:13.471 --> 10:15.029
Anyone with him?

10:16.021 --> 10:17.692
No, no, not that I saw.

10:17.756 --> 10:19.358
No?

10:21.628 --> 10:23.933
No, I never saw him.

10:27.020 --> 10:28.521
You sure?

10:29.285 --> 10:31.277
Yes. Yes, I'm sure.
I never saw him.

10:35.498 --> 10:37.133
Thank you!

10:38.780 --> 10:42.058
♪♪

10:49.394 --> 10:50.562
All done.

10:55.481 --> 10:58.466
