10:59.654 --> 11:02.802
Nicky's already on the boat.
She's heading north to Newport.

11:02.903 --> 11:04.161
She'll draw the Coast Guard,

11:04.209 --> 11:06.472
which means they'll be 20 miles
away by the time we board.

11:06.519 --> 11:08.820
What if she chickens out?
She won't.

11:10.864 --> 11:12.050
Jet skis?

11:12.216 --> 11:14.028
Yeah, all gassed up,
running great.

11:14.153 --> 11:16.302
- Boat?
- Anchored where we said.

11:16.809 --> 11:18.613
So you guys will
scuttle the jet skis,

11:18.668 --> 11:20.864
and then you'll take the boats
backs to the marina.

11:21.052 --> 11:23.059
Yep.
Then we're good.

11:23.731 --> 11:26.528
You keep your heads
and we keep professional.

11:26.802 --> 11:28.883
Professional?

11:29.309 --> 11:31.481
It's a smash and grab
on the water, bro.

11:31.668 --> 11:34.363
We're goddamn pirates.

11:35.395 --> 11:37.622
Once I stop the boat,

11:38.317 --> 11:41.598
I'll kill the phones
and the radio with this.

11:42.005 --> 11:45.098
The whole deal should take
less than 15 minutes.

11:45.513 --> 11:47.153
Threaten the bride and groom.

11:47.348 --> 11:49.427
That should shut everyone up.
Okay?

11:49.623 --> 11:51.934
Okay.
Any questions?

11:53.958 --> 11:56.466
All right. Thanks.

11:56.981 --> 11:58.746
Thanks?

11:59.450 --> 12:00.473
Yeah, you're right.

12:00.567 --> 12:02.523
All right,
well, don't screw this up.

12:02.571 --> 12:03.911
Otherwise, I'm gonna kick
all your asses.

12:03.958 --> 12:05.004
Does that work for you?

12:05.052 --> 12:06.107
That's good.

12:06.192 --> 12:07.855
I gotta get to work.

12:08.052 --> 12:10.848
I'll see you guys back here.
Drinks are on Deran.

12:19.238 --> 12:20.692
Are you gonna eat?

12:20.856 --> 12:22.533
I'm not hungry.

12:50.511 --> 12:52.237
You got Baz. Leave a message.

12:52.684 --> 12:55.308
You're gonna have to start
taking some responsibility, Baz.

12:55.356 --> 12:57.395
I can't do this alone.

12:57.637 --> 12:59.215
Call me back.

13:05.013 --> 13:08.410
