25:24.413 --> 25:26.121
Get in there!

25:29.163 --> 25:30.660
You do not look at me.

25:30.829 --> 25:33.363
- You hear me?
- Yes! Yes!

25:35.886 --> 25:37.355
Oh, my God. Oh, my God.
Oh, my God.

25:37.403 --> 25:38.403
Shut up.

25:43.493 --> 25:46.162
