down on the ground!

25:48.932 --> 25:50.653
Everybody, get down!

25:50.701 --> 25:52.755
Todos al piso! Todos al piso!

25:52.903 --> 25:54.871
Oh, my God! No!

25:54.905 --> 25:56.256
It's okay. It's okay. Don't cry.
Don't cry, it's okay.

25:57.412 --> 25:58.795
On the ground.
Tell them to get on the ground.

25:58.842 --> 26:00.724
- Todos al piso!
- Hey!

26:00.772 --> 26:02.020
Todos al piso!

26:02.169 --> 26:03.794
