26:18.461 --> 26:21.031
- nadie se va herir!
- Uh, Yellow Tie. Yellow Tie.

26:21.325 --> 26:23.466
Hey, hands around your back.
Now.

26:24.836 --> 26:26.289
Al piso!

26:27.096 --> 26:28.843
Everybody, stay down!

26:29.475 --> 26:33.613
Okay, if everybody stays calm,
nobody gets hurt.

26:34.077 --> 26:35.559
Okay.

26:36.226 --> 26:37.710
